# Mapbox GL JS public access token (starts with pk.).
# Copy this file to .env.local and paste your token. .env.local is gitignored.
# Get one at https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/ and URL-restrict it.
# WITHOUT a token the map still works, falling back to tokenless raster basemaps
# (OSM for "Peta", Esri imagery for "Satelit").
VITE_MAPBOX_TOKEN=pk.your_public_token_here
